-- Daimler Prepares Hostile Takeover Defense, Automobilwoche Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-04-29T13:15:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/daimler-prepares-hostile-takeover-defense-automobilwoche-says.html
Daimler AG (DAI)  has prepared measures to
complicate continued operation at the company in the case of a
hostile takeover, Automobilwoche  reported , without saying where
it got the information.  Measures include an agreement with banks allowing them to
withdraw credit facilities of more than 8 billion euros in case
of a takeover, Automobilwoche said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
